  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to measure whether high-density electroencephalography can
      improve the detection of electrophysiological signs of awareness compared to conventional
      electroencephalography in post-anoxic comatose patients
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
